cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.ST

This paper is about a machine learning framework that deals with a wide range of loss functions and has provable generalization guarantees. This suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and statistics (cs.ST).
